# denylist.example - copy to denylist.local (gitignored) and fill in for real.
#
# One term or extended-regex pattern per line; lines starting with # are
# comments. The pre-commit hook and scripts/leak-audit.sh join these with |
# and grep case-insensitively. Put in everything that must never appear in
# this public repo: unreleased product codenames, studio and client names,
# personal domains, home paths, and live-key shapes.
#
# NEVER commit the real list: your list of secrets is itself a secret.
my-unreleased-codename
my-studio-name
my-client-name
mydomain\.example
/Users/<your-username>
sk-[A-Za-z0-9]{16,}
sk_live_[A-Za-z0-9]+
pk_live_[A-Za-z0-9]+
